songs.title: Osama
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
My niggas ride like Al Qaeda
My niggas ride like Al Qaeda
My niggas ride like Al Qaeda
My niggas ride like Al Qaeda
My niggas ride like Al Qaeda


[Chorus]
My niggas ride like Al Qaeda
You think it's cheaper to keep her
You think it’s cheaper to keep her
I ride with dope like it's legal
My niggas got with Osama
My niggas strapped with Osama
My niggas strapped with Osama
My niggas strapped with Osama
Young niggas strapped with Osama
The young niggas got with Osama

The young niggas  strapped with that blatt blatt blatt

You niggas ain't nothin’ but bitch niggas
You niggas ain't nothin' but snitch niggas
You niggas ain't nothin' but hoe niggas
You niggas ain't nothin' but broke niggas
You want to come around act like you don't know niggas
I’ma let the .44 kiss you, I’ma let my bottom hoe hit you
I be hangin' round some toe taggers
Had it smellin’ like some clam chowder
Transportin' like a space pilot
I got bands on me ain't got no wallet
I got xans on me I got plenty molly
Got young niggas and they suicidal
Got my young niggas that's my moulinyan
Hit you with the nickel, fuck a snow bunny
Hit you with the nickel have your soul running
I just walk around with a check
She a fuck my friend for a check (I know she will)
I know money mean everything to you baby
But you gotta have respect
Hold Up, hold up

My niggas ride like Al Qaeda
You think it’s cheaper to keep her
You think it's cheaper to keep her
I ride with dope like it's legal
My niggas got with Osama
My niggas strapped with Osama
My niggas strapped with Osama
My niggas strapped with Osama
My niggas strapped with Osama
The young niggas strapped with Osama
The young niggas got with Osama
Strapped nigga strapped with Osama
The young niggas strapped with that blatt blatt blatt


[Verse 2]
I'm strapped like Osama
My pockets got llama I'm fresh in Balmains
I trap out the Hummer, say fuck all the drama, I'm bustin' your brain
Ain't trustin' you bitches
Ain't trustin' these bitches you fuckin' for fame
No love for these niggas no love in this game
Used to steal at the store
Used to skip school and go jump on the train
(used to jump on the train)
I go fuck on your hoe
Fuck being broke I got money I made
I go stand on that corner
I was never afraid I was never afraid
I go hit off a lick, I go juug off a brick, I got money to make
I got ways to get paid I get straight to that check
I get money I'm fresh (I get money I'm fresh)
You didn't know [?] you my nigga for life

[Chorus]
My niggas ride like Al Qaeda
You think it's cheaper to keep her
You think it's cheaper to keep her
I ride with dope like it's legal
My niggas strapped with Osama
My niggas strapped with Osama
